Structural Defense
------------------------------------------------------------------------

scyBorg is governed by three independent nonprofits:
  - Free Software Foundation (AGPL-3.0)
  - Open RPG Creative Foundation (ORC)
  - Creative Commons (CC-BY-SA 4.0)

No single entity can revoke any of these licenses.
This is structural, not contractual.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
Provenance Trio (Enforcement Layer)
------------------------------------------------------------------------

The provenance trio provides machine-verifiable evidence for scyBorg:
  - sweetGrass: who created what (BY in CC-BY-SA)
  - rhizoCrypt: derivation chains (SA in CC-BY-SA)
  - loamSpine: immutable license certificates

Evidence, not enforcement. Copyright law is the enforcement mechanism.

